item.content:encoded: 1st batch of PUC results marked excellence in performance. Out of 45 students, Menaz Parveen secured distinction marks 522 ( 87%), 34 – First Class, 8 – Second class, 1 Pass class. The results have shown dedicated service rendered by lecturers and disciplined effort by the students. A Felicitation function was held on 15th May 2013 for honouring students and staff.
